1. Make and make install libfxp in libfxp/
2. Change mysql settings in src/ftpcrawler.h
3. Run make
4. Copy the contents of the www directory somewhere to your wwwroot, change inc/config.inc.ph
5. Create a mysql database, with the same name as you enterd in the configs.
6. mysql -p database -u user --password << ftplist.sql
